Ranger Help for: guide
======================

SYNTAX:      guide <player>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to guide another player through the terrain,
granting them a dodge bonus while the Ranger leads. The guided player
benefits from the Ranger's knowledge of the land, receiving improved
evasion as the Ranger directs them through safe paths and advantageous
positions. The guide effect lasts as long as both players remain in the
same room. This is a useful support skill for group play.
